V0609_01_00_00_0.text: It's a pleasure to meet you.

V0609_01_00_01_0.text: Allow me to test your abilities with a Speed Duel.

V0609_01_00_02_0.text: Speed Duels are quite thrilling, aren't they.

V0609_01_00_03_0.text: There are consequences for interfering with our plans.

V0609_01_00_04_0.text: If you believe you can defeat me, you are welcome to try.

V0609_01_00_05_0.text: So you've decided that I'm the weakest of the Hanoi?

V0609_01_00_06_0.text: I will do whatever I must to serve Master Varis.

V0609_01_00_07_0.text: Playmaker, I will personally bring your existence to an end.

V0609_01_00_08_0.text: Your misguided sense of justice will be your downfall.

V0609_01_00_09_0.text: Care to spare a moment with your biggest fan, Blue Angel?

V0609_01_00_10_0.text: Your Dueling has charmed players worldwide - including me.

V0609_01_00_11_0.text:
You think you'll win?
There must be a bug in your program.

V0609_01_00_12_0.text: If you wish to Duel me, who am I to refuse.

V0609_03_00_00_0.text: You must realize this Duel will not end well for you.

V0609_03_00_01_0.text:
Am I supposed to be afraid of your attacks?
Because I'm not.

V0609_03_00_02_0.text: I thought your goal was to defeat me - not lose in shame.

V0609_03_00_04_0.text: There are so many things I can't wait to do.

V0609_03_00_05_0.text:
Ooh - you seem ready to counterattack.
I better be careful.

V0609_03_00_06_0.text: I can honestly say I'm impressed with your moves!

V0609_03_00_07_0.text:
Hahaha!
That's an excellent strategy - but not perfect!

V0609_05_00_00_0.text: Allow me to show you respect by completely annihilating you.

V0609_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over the card I Set!

V0609_07_09_01_0.text: This is the card I Set.

V0609_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0609_11_10_01_0.text: Watch as I manifest my circuit!

V0609_11_10_02_1.text:
I set my monsters in the Link Arrows!
Link the circuit!

V0609_16_00_01_0.text: You disappoint me with your incompetence.

V0609_16_00_02_0.text: Since you are out of options, I will end this Duel.

V0609_21_00_00_0.text: It's clear you're unable to see the forest for the trees.

V0609_21_00_01_1.text: You're in a tough spot, but I hope you keep trying to win.

V0609_21_00_02_0.text:
Losing this Duel means you will lose everything.
Good luck.

V0609_21_00_03_0.text: With that, I end my turn.

V0609_21_00_03_1.text: This Duel is trending towards your defeat.

V0609_21_00_04_1.text: If you're planning to try something, you should do it soon.

V0609_21_00_05_0.text: You haven't broken my strategy yet.

V0609_21_00_06_0.text: What you've done is spectacular - at least on the surface.

V0609_28_00_00_0.text:
There's a simple reason why you lost.
You're not me.

V0609_28_00_01_0.text: Your Dueling is so hideous that it makes me ill.

V0609_28_00_02_0.text: How kind of you to offer me this victory as a gift.

V0609_28_00_03_0.text:
You need talent and technique to win.
You have neither.

V0609_28_00_04_0.text: You had me worried for a moment, but I see everything.

V0609_28_00_05_0.text: Please leave so you can stop wasting my time.

V0609_28_00_06_0.text:
You think I'm horrible?
That I go too far?
Why - thank you!

V0609_28_00_06_1.text: It proves you're not willing to do whatever it takes to win!

V0609_28_00_07_0.text:
Don't feel bad.
Not everyone can be the best.

V0609_28_00_09_0.text: You need to learn not to fear pain - but to embrace it.

V0609_28_00_10_0.text: You won't feel guilty for failing to defeat me.

V0609_28_00_10_1.text: Because you can’t feel emotions if you don’t exist.

V0609_28_00_11_0.text: You have the heart of a champion - but not the talent.

V0609_28_00_12_0.text: I quite enjoyed my experience in the Lost Incident.

V0609_28_00_12_1.text: But seeing how you're glaring at me, you must have not.

V0609_28_00_13_0.text: It was truly an honor to Duel you in your final Duel ever.

V0609_28_00_14_0.text: You're here to save me, but you couldn't even save yourself.

V0609_28_00_15_0.text: I'm not so dumb to base my whole life on a fairy tale!

V0609_28_00_16_0.text: Unlike a children’s book, life doesn't have happy endings.

V0609_28_00_16_1.text:
Most of ‘em?
They end in tragedy!

V0609_28_00_17_0.text: I'd ask for any last words, but we've reached the last page.

V0609_28_00_17_1.text:
It was quite a good tale.
But no one is writing a sequel.

V0609_28_00_18_0.text: One Duelist receives glory - and the other misery.

V0609_28_00_19_0.text: Are you called Blue Angel because you always feel blue?

V0609_28_00_20_0.text: Our names may be similar, but our skills clearly are not.

V0609_28_00_21_0.text: Everything I do is for you, Master Varis.

V0609_28_00_22_0.text:
You gave me a home, Master Varis.
I will never betray you.

V0609_28_00_23_0.text: It's interesting how our decks are fundamentally the same.

V0609_28_00_24_0.text: I didn’t know it was possible to program arrogance.

V0609_28_00_25_0.text: You Ignis may pretend to be sophisticated creatures.

V0609_28_00_25_1.text:
But you’re like every program.
Predictable and formulaic.

V0609_28_00_26_0.text: You can't be smart when you're limited by your programming.

V0609_28_00_27_0.text: When my Ignis was deleted, I was surprised to feel its loss.

V0609_29_00_00_0.text: How dare you harm those who protected me!

V0609_29_00_01_0.text: What right do you have to chop my trees down!

V0609_29_00_02_0.text: I know I'm not the strongest, but I have fulfilled my duty.

V0609_29_00_03_0.text: I shouldn't have let my opponent goad me into mistakes.

V0609_29_00_04_0.text: Master Varis, forgive me for my incompetence...

V0609_29_00_06_0.text: You never cease to impress me, Master Varis.

V0609_33_00_01_0.text: Are you capable of defeating me?

V0609_30_00_02_0.text: Ah, impressive. So that's what you were going for.

V0609_34_00_00_0.text: Is that supposed to worry me?

V0609_34_00_02_0.text: Will that card make me realize the error of my ways?

V0609_34_00_03_0.text: Try harder to understand why I am how I am!

V0609_34_00_04_0.text: I know you will save my soul!

V0609_34_00_05_0.text: Oh my. I didn't realize I still had this card.

V0609_34_00_06_0.text: After all your confidence, you have no way to defeat me.

V0609_34_00_08_0.text: Now's my chance to take everything from you!

V0609_34_00_09_0.text:
You think I play dirty?
Thank you for the compliment.

V0609_34_00_10_0.text: If you want to attack, go right ahead!

V0609_34_00_11_0.text:
You're not going to do anything?
But I was hoping you would.

V0609_34_00_12_0.text: You have the courage of a coward!

V0609_34_00_14_0.text:
Your attack was unsuccessful.
What will you do now?

V0609_34_00_15_0.text: Though you're my opponent, I can respect a smart strategy.

V0609_34_00_16_0.text: Have you ever seen such a beautiful field?

V0609_34_00_17_0.text:
I've never seen you so upset.
I like it.

V0609_34_00_18_0.text:
I take what I want.
That's how I Duel.

V0609_32_00_01_0.text:
A warning:
If you enter Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links, you'll have to battle me.
If this is not a deterrence, please feel free to enter.

V0609_35_00_00_0.text:
My name is Spectre.
Pleasure to make your acquaintance.

V0609_35_00_01_0.text: I live to serve Master Varis.

V0609_36_00_00_0.text: I'm sure you can handle the rest of this Duel.

V0609_36_00_03_0.text: I trust you will end this Duel, Master Varis.

V0609_08_00_00_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Sunvine Sowing!

V0609_08_00_01_0.text: I activate my Continuous Spell, Sunvine Cross Breed!

V0609_08_00_02_0.text: I activate Sunvine Cross Breed's effect!

V0609_08_00_03_0.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Sunvine Shrine!

V0609_08_00_05_0.text: I send Sunvine Shrine to the Graveyard to use its effect!

V0609_08_00_06_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Sunavalon Bloom!

V0609_08_00_07_0.text: The Continuous Trap, Sunavalon Bloom's effect!

V0609_08_00_08_0.text: Have you read the fairy tale about the blue angel?

V0609_08_00_08_1.text: I activate my Spell Card, Angel of Blue Tears!

V0609_08_00_09_0.text: Is the blue angel crying due to sadness - or due to joy?

V0609_08_00_09_1.text: I banish Angel of Blue Tears from the Graveyard!

V0609_09_00_00_0.text: Link Summoning Sunavalon Dryatrentiay activates its effect!

V0609_09_00_02_0.text:
That was pointless.
I activate Sunavalon Dryanome's effect!

V0609_09_00_03_0.text: Dryanome is linked to that monster, so its effect activates!

V0609_09_00_04_0.text: Sunavalon Melias's effect activates when it's Link Summoned!

V0609_09_00_07_0.text: Since I took damage, Sunavalon Dryades's effect activates!

V0609_09_00_08_0.text: Using Genius Loci to Link Summon activates Dryas's effect!

V0609_09_00_09_0.text: If I take damage, Sunavalon Dryas can activate its effect!

V0609_09_00_10_0.text: My Sunvine Gardna is linked to a Sunavalon Link Monster!

V0609_09_00_11_0.text: Sunvine Gardna activates when it's destroyed in battle!

V0609_09_00_12_0.text: Special Summoning Sunvine Thrasher activates its effect!

V0609_09_00_13_1.text: And due to its effect, that monster is now mine!

V0609_09_00_14_0.text: Special Summoning Sunvine Healer activates its effect!

V0609_09_00_15_0.text: When a Plant Link Monster deals damage, my Healer activates!

V0609_09_00_16_0.text: I activate Sunvine Maiden's effect from my hand!

V0609_09_00_17_0.text: Sunseed Shadow's effect activates from my hand!

V0609_09_00_18_0.text: I banish Sunseed Shadow from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0609_09_00_19_0.text: When Sunseed Twin is Summoned, its effect activates!

V0609_09_00_20_0.text: Sunseed Twin activates its effect from the Graveyard!

V0609_09_00_21_0.text: I send Dark Angel from my hand to the Graveyard!

V0609_13_00_00_0.text:
Rise before me!
Link 4 Sunavalon Dryatrentiay!

V0609_13_00_06_0.text:
Join the Duel!
Link 1 Sunvine Gardna!

V0609_13_00_13_0.text: I shall unlock your heart and release your deepest desires.

V0609_19_00_00_0.text: Sunavalon Dryatrentiay will protect me by attacking you!

V0609_48_00_00_0.text: It's an honor to Duel you.

V0609_27_00_02_0.text: How can this be happening to me...
